  "key_invariants": [
    "WorkspaceID hashes the symlink-resolved absolute path (SHA-256, 20 bytes, hex); case-insensitive filesystems (macOS, Windows) lowercase the path before hashing",
    "AcquireOwnerLock uses unix.Flock LOCK_EX|LOCK_NB; returns ErrWorkspaceOwned immediately if the lock is held",
    "WriteOwnerRecord and WriteLayoutVersion are atomic: write to temp, fsync, chmod 0600, rename",
    "PrepareWorkspace admission order: AcquireOwnerLock -> EnsureLayoutVersion -> ValidateOrReclaimOwner; any failure releases the lock",
    "ValidateOrReclaimOwner assumes caller holds owner.lock; checks pid+socket liveness before removing stale owner.json",
    "Windows stubs for AcquireOwnerLock, StartEmbeddedPostgres, ProcessAlive, SocketHealthy, StopEmbeddedPostgres all return errors or false — local runtime is Unix-only",
    "ResolveWorkspaceRoot walks ancestors for .pcg.yaml first, then .git; falls back to startDir",
    "PCG_HOME overrides the default per-OS home root (darwin: ~/Library/Application Support/pcg, linux: $XDG_DATA_HOME/pcg or ~/.local/share/pcg, windows: %LOCALAPPDATA%/pcg)"
  ],
